Logging framework::

sl4j, logback,log4j

Destination create logging in some file.
 
3 componenets:

Logger,Appender,Layout

Get the logger object and get some appender(ex: file,console,rollingfile(we specify size of file) appender)
Levels::: Fatal , Error, Warn, Info, debug, trace..  ON/OFF for levels
if we say logging level=debug (Fatal , Error, Warn, Info, debug)then we mean all till debug is logged.

HOW TO DO:::
1) Get hold of logger.
2)In conf file we will specify logging level.

